{"tid":632222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美空襲敘利亞 中國網友留言盼給北京來一發 然後他就...","createTime":"2018-04-17T07:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T11:35:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b1e1039942dda637632b68c492bcd2a5772b81","tid":632222,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/154253_4202ac4eb8290348dc48cf2b97a5f122.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F154253_4202ac4eb8290348dc48cf2b97a5f122.png&h=1c2900f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/154302_5395abd648e991042f44d01f480ed27d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F154302_5395abd648e991042f44d01f480ed27d.png&h=878beef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/154316_22e997e8e8b23349e678e9b48aa797a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F154316_22e997e8e8b23349e678e9b48aa797a5.png&h=a07945be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕為懲戒敘利亞總統阿塞德濫用化武屠殺平民，美國總統川普14日凌晨下令，聯手英法兩國同步對敘國發動「精準攻擊」，發射逾百枚飛彈，轟炸3處化武設施，有攝影微博分享飛彈劃破夜空的照片，不過有中國網友在底下留言：「希望給北京來一個。」立刻遭到當局逮捕，該帳號也被直接刪除。<br />\n微博「頂尖攝影觀賞」日前分享一張外媒所拍攝的美軍空襲敘利亞照片，只見大馬士革上空突然出現數枚飛彈劃破天際，照亮夜空，直襲目標，本來只是單純的分享壯觀照片，但有位帳號為「陳棟良」的中國網友在底下留言：「希望給北京來一個。」立刻被當局掌握，帶走調查。<br />\n四川警方發布聲明表示，遂寧市一名17歲的陳姓少年，在微博上發布不當言論，目前已被公安機關帶回接受調查；其他網友也發現該帳號也已遭刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2398028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2398028&d=u%2BkFq2YMDkcNMG79MupW%2BIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e07fef2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2398028&h=9b229c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2398028</a>"},{"pid":"c72968dbebb0d9cd3aeeb655b092ae525f70cc87","tid":632222,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"下世小心d"},{"pid":"8f5f55ef6ab36d918db9d7464ea58c77c6e7dc9d","tid":632222,"uid":60655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  言論自由"},{"pid":"2a7ea1b05f936bce166e709aa3034cf9b56c55de","tid":632222,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"網絡警察 洛克人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f19fba8ad06f5f938f2e5fef4f0fed9876757c","tid":632222,"uid":89543,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/155354_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F155354_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=25bdc172&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63e3a1bd15eb04a79e1feb048f8876032ddf1bac","tid":632222,"uid":93784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"微博實名制+綁埋手機號碼 = 實捉到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0efb2398545062239b9900a04deaafe4ef8c167","tid":632222,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"頭盔都唔戴"},{"pid":"0eabea99be75d08717310d87e1bc5c445fd94fed","tid":632222,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲d 香港係咪都係咁"},{"pid":"e379d474e67d590533369f05836b0b4569de9eda","tid":632222,"uid":93784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:0